---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { SITE } from "../../site-config";
---

<Layout
  title={`${SITE.author.fullName} - Projects - Document Q&A (RAG)`}
  description="Upload a PDF and ask questions about it. Uses sentence-transformers, FAISS, and a Hugging Face-hosted LLM."
>
  <main class="w-full min-h-screen px-4 py-8 md:px-8 md:py-12 text-white max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <a
      href="/projects"
      class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-primary-100 hover:text-primary-100 bg-darkslate-900 hover:bg-darkslate-800 hover:border-primary-500 w-fit px-4 py-2 border border-darkslate-400 rounded-lg transition-all duration-200"
      >← Back</a
    >

    <div class="mt-10 mb-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-neutral-50 mb-3">
        Document Q&A (RAG)
      </h1>
      <p class="text-neutral-300 text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-3xl">
        Upload a PDF, index its contents, and ask questions against the document.
        The app uses sentence-transformers for embeddings, FAISS for retrieval,
        and a Hugging Face-hosted LLM for grounded answers.
      </p>
    </div>

    <section class="grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-2 mb-8">
      <article class="group rounded-lg border border-darkslate-400 hover:border-primary-500 bg-darkslate-500 p-6 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
          <div class="w-1 h-6 bg-gradient-to-b from-primary-400 to-primary-700 rounded-full"></div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-100">Project Overview</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-neutral-300 leading-relaxed">
          A demo-friendly retrieval pipeline that turns a static PDF into an interactive
          question-answering experience with document-aware responses.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="group rounded-lg border border-darkslate-400 hover:border-primary-500 bg-darkslate-500 p-6 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
          <div class="w-1 h-6 bg-gradient-to-b from-primary-400 to-primary-700 rounded-full"></div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-100">Tech Stack</h2>
        </div>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li class="text-neutral-300 flex items-center"><span class="mr-3">→</span> sentence-transformers embeddings</li>
          <li class="text-neutral-300 flex items-center"><span class="mr-3">→</span> FAISS vector retrieval</li>
          <li class="text-neutral-300 flex items-center"><span class="mr-3">→</span> Hugging Face-hosted LLM</li>
          <li class="text-neutral-300 flex items-center"><span class="mr-3">→</span> PDF upload and Q&A workflow</li>
        </ul>
      </article>
    </section>

    <section class="rounded-lg border border-darkslate-400 hover:border-primary-500 bg-darkslate-500 p-6 mb-8 transition-all duration-300">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
        <div class="w-1 h-7 bg-gradient-to-b from-primary-400 to-primary-700 rounded-full"></div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-100">Key Features</h2>
      </div>
      <ul class="space-y-2 ml-3">
        <li class="text-neutral-300 flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-primary-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0">✓</span>
          <span>Upload a PDF and extract searchable chunks automatically</span>
        </li>
        <li class="text-neutral-300 flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-primary-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0">✓</span>
          <span>Retrieve the most relevant passages with FAISS similarity search</span>
        </li>
        <li class="text-neutral-300 flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-primary-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0">✓</span>
          <span>Generate grounded answers from the uploaded document context</span>
        </li>
        <li class="text-neutral-300 flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-primary-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0">✓</span>
          <span>Simple interface that works well as a portfolio demo</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="rounded-lg border border-darkslate-400 hover:border-primary-500 bg-darkslate-500 p-6 transition-all duration-300">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
        <div class="w-1 h-7 bg-gradient-to-b from-primary-400 to-primary-700 rounded-full"></div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-100">Project Focus</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="text-neutral-300 leading-relaxed">
        This project is designed to showcase practical RAG fundamentals: document ingestion,
        chunking, embedding generation, vector search, and answer synthesis from retrieved context.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="rounded-lg border border-darkslate-400 hover:border-primary-500 bg-darkslate-500 p-6 mt-8 transition-all duration-300">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
        <div class="w-1 h-7 bg-gradient-to-b from-primary-400 to-primary-700 rounded-full"></div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-100">Project Links</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <a
          href="https://huggingface.co/spaces/hamza100x/Document-QA-RAG"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="group/btn inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-primary-100 bg-darkslate-900 hover:bg-darkslate-800 hover:border-primary-500 px-5 py-2.5 border border-darkslate-400 rounded-lg transition-all duration-200"
        >
          <span>Live Demo</span>
          <span class="group-hover/btn:translate-x-1 transition-transform duration-200">↗</span>
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://github.com/hamza100x/document-qa-rag"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="group/btn inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-primary-100 bg-darkslate-900 hover:bg-darkslate-800 hover:border-primary-500 px-5 py-2.5 border border-darkslate-400 rounded-lg transition-all duration-200"
        >
          <span>Source Code</span>
          <span class="group-hover/btn:translate-x-1 transition-transform duration-200">→</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<script>
  document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", () => {
    const loader = document.querySelector(".loader");
    if (loader) {
      loader.remove();
    }
  });
</script>
